response.overview: More than 60 percent of Australians have never heard of quolls or even know what they are. Meet Paul, a passionate quoll lover and the founder of QuollSA. He shares with us his love for quolls, his conservation activities, and how important it is to help protect these marsupial predators as they are close to facing the deadly risk of extinction.
response.tagline: An animal that no one knows about is about to go extinct.
response.title: Chasing Quolls
